parameters: \FF[sumire_trouble2]Sumire: "Mmm...ahh...♪ This is so wrong...yet..."
\FF[sumire_trouble2]Sumire: "...Akane-san!? What are you doing here!?"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "Hello... Are you okay?"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "I-I'm fine!! It's just that...my body is feeling a
bit hot..."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "I'm sorry you had to see me like this..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "(Her clothes aren't disheveled, so she wasn't
masturbating. But she does seem feverish...and somehow
sensual...)"

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "This isn't like you, Sumire... You seemed so out
of it. You're in the infirmary, after all... You shouldn't
push yourself too hard."

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "Yes... I'll do that. I've gotten myself too deeply
involved..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "Too deeply involved? As the president of the
Detective Club, I can't just ignore that statement."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "(As an agent of Banter, it seems Ms. Oomurasaki has
been investigating something related to Poison. That must be
connected to... her friend Seiryu-san.)"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "Could it be... you've stepped into another
world...?"
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "!!"

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Akane, don't start with such outlandish topics.
Another world... this isn't a manga, you know..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "Ugh...ughhh...♪ Let me give you one piece of
advice... If you're..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "If you're following the same case as me... don't
enter 'The Kingdom'..."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "Otherwise, you'll end up suffering like I did..."
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "'The Kingdom'!? Is there a monster there!?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "So it really is another world! I was bluffing,
but... nothing else explains that kind of movement!"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "...? What are you two talking about...?"
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "How do I get there!? Tell me what to do...!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "I've warned you... It would be best if you withdrew
from this matter. Otherwise, 'the mummy hunter will become
the mummy'..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "I can't just stand by and do nothing! I have to stop
it!!"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Then explain it to me properly! Both of you!"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "..."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "(Even if I explain it to Nadeshiko-san, she
probably won't believe me. It would only cause more
confusion...)"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "(I don't want to involve Nadeshiko any further... If
I'm going to another world to vanquish it, I must go
alone!)"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "...Why are you both silent?"
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[2]Sumire: "..."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Akane: "..."
\F[nako_trouble]\FF[sumire_trouble2]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Ughh~...!"
A

parameters:
Mikoto: "Good day, my lost little lamb. Do you need my
advice again for a brighter future?"

Mikoto: "It must be tough to find all the suspects scattered
around the school. You know, you can let me help you."

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(It feels like she's seen right through me again...
What should I do...?)"
Ask
I'll stop
聞く
\F[beni_angry2]Akane: "Oh, could you tell me...?"

Mikoto: "Of course, it's no trouble at all♪ First, you'll
find Washio-sensei on the 3rd floor of the west school
building. In classroom 2-B on the 2nd floor, there's Seiryu-
san."

Mikoto: "Kamegami-san is in the AV room, and Satsuki-san is
by the school gate. Once you've met all of them, Ayaka-san
will appear in the 3rd floor corridor."

Mikoto: "But be careful. I have a bad feeling about what
happens after you talk to her... Take care, okay?"
\F[beni_smile]Akane: "U-understood. Thank you very much..."

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "(If a teacher is worried about me, that's genuinely
scary... I need to be careful...)"
やめておく

Mikoto: "Oh, is that so. That's too bad. If you ever want to
ask again, feel free to come by anytime♪"

Mikoto: "Nyururu~♪ You've arrived. Are you searching for
naughty children who haven't yet become slippery slaves?
Allow me to assist you♪"

\F[beni_close1]Akane: "Nyururu~♪ So there are still some kids that
Nadeshiko failed to catch, huh? Teacher is really useful
after all♪"

Mikoto: "Yes! We must corrupt them as soon as possible... or
we can't make those children happy♪ Ahhh...♪ I want to take
them to the locker in the infirmary quickly♪"
Ask
I'll stop
聞く

Mikoto: "Alright. First, the rooftop. Suzuran-san is there
with Shidou-san. Separate them and lead them to corruption♪"

Mikoto: "At the school gates, there's Seiryu patrol officer.
She's Seiryu-san's older sister."

Mikoto: "Don't overlook the child who doesn't belong in the
staff room, Kamegami-san♪ And nearby is Yamanoi-sensei too♪"

Mikoto: "Let's ambush Nozawa-san in the student council
room♪ Everyone should be willing to help♪"

Mikoto: "We must hurry to the chemistry room... to save Lord
Closille from Hanamura-san's evil clutches♪"

Mikoto: "Once you've corrupted those five people, Shiratora-
san should be back at the entrance♪ Let's report our
successes to each other♪"

\F[beni_close1]Akane: "I see... Nyururu~♪ With this, we won't let anyone
escape...♪"

Mikoto: "Exactly. Everyone becomes a happy comrade♪ We can't
let even a single one get away♪ Fufufu...♪"
\F[beni_close1]Akane: "Fufufu...♪"
やめておく

\F[beni_close1]Akane: "Thank you! But I'll find and corrupt them on my
own!"

Mikoto: "Understood! But if you need help, don't hesitate to
ask❤"
